<rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>NuGet on Code it Yourself...</title><link>https://carlos.mendible.com/tags/nuget/</link><description>Recent content in NuGet on Code it Yourself...</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>en-us</language><copyright>Copyright &amp;copy; 2020 - Carlos Mendible</copyright><lastBuildDate>Thu, 09 May 2013 10:31:14 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://carlos.mendible.com/tags/nuget/feed.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Private Nuget Server responds with (405) Method Not Allowed while pushing or deleting a package</title><link>https://carlos.mendible.com/2013/05/09/private-nuget-server-responds-with-405-method-not-allowed-while-pushing-or-deleting-a-package/</link><pubDate>Thu, 09 May 2013 10:31:14 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://carlos.mendible.com/2013/05/09/private-nuget-server-responds-with-405-method-not-allowed-while-pushing-or-deleting-a-package/</guid><description>&lt;p>So you&amp;rsquo;ve deployed your own private &lt;strong>NuGet&lt;/strong> server to &lt;strong>IIS&lt;/strong> but you get this annoying exception trying to push packages:&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;strong>(405) Method Not Allowed&lt;/strong>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>Well as stated in many web pages removing &lt;strong>WebDAVModule&lt;/strong> does fix the issue, but &lt;strong>be sure you add the configuration in the right section!&lt;/strong> (not in the &lt;strong>elmah&lt;/strong> section) or the fix wont work!&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4">&lt;code class="language-html" data-lang="html">&amp;lt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672">configuration&lt;/span>&amp;gt;
&amp;lt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672">system.webServer&lt;/span>&amp;gt;
&amp;lt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672">validation&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">validateIntegratedModeConfiguration&lt;/span>&lt;span style="color:#f92672">=&lt;/span>&lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#34;false&amp;#34;&lt;/span> /&amp;gt;
&amp;lt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672">modules&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">runAllManagedModulesForAllRequests&lt;/span>&lt;span style="color:#f92672">=&lt;/span>&lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#34;true&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&amp;gt;
&amp;lt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672">remove&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">name&lt;/span>&lt;span style="color:#f92672">=&lt;/span>&lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#34;WebDAVModule&amp;#34;&lt;/span> /&amp;gt;
&amp;lt;/&lt;span style="color:#f92672">modules&lt;/span>&amp;gt;
...
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div></description></item></channel></rss>